#~ msgid ""
#~ "&quot;Buckle!&quot; you think, it is of course <classname>MyClass</"
#~ "classname>. You go to line 3902, and instead of trying to find the word "
#~ "in the text, you launch the Editing Command Dialog, enter <userinput>s/"
