#~ msgstr "Substitución de texto en todo o documento"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Imagine that you have a file, in which you mention a <quote>Miss Jensen</"
#~ "quote> several times, when someone comes in and tells you that she just "
#~ "got married to <quote>Mr Jones</quote>. You want, of course, to replace "
#~ "each and every occurrence of <quote>Miss Jensen</quote> with <quote>Ms "
#~ "Jones</quote>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Imaxine que ten un documento no que menciona a <quote>Dona Helena</quote> "
#~ "varias veces, e vai alguén e lle di que a muller cambiou o nome, e agora "
#~ "se chama «Iria». En canto sae do teu asombro, decátase de que lle vai "
#~ "tocar cambiar todas as aparicións do nome no documento."

